description: Listen to Pat Metheny describe what he has in store for the 2012 Pat Metheny Summer Music Workshop.  This special event is a rare opportunity to study in an intimate setting with Pat, as well as legendary drummer, Jack DeJohnette, and bassist, Larry Grenadier. Pat will also play in a special duo concert with Jim Hall.  This workshop is open to any intermediate to advanced jazz musician. For more details, or to register for this event, contact National Music Workshop at 800-234-6479 or visit http://www.guitarworkshop.com/artist-metheny.php
